element.name: Cache 'n' Coffee #001 by Kersti.com, Event Cache (1/1)

description.b:
Come join us from 7:00 PM to unwind and sip beverages from the
bean while swapping tales, coins and bugs.

element.long-description: All are welcome to attend, especially any newbies or visitors. Please post how many people with each "Will Attend." Coordinates are to the location. Food and drink is on your own. The event is later in the evening to accommodate those who wish to stay for dinner. The venue is child friendly so bring those ankle biters too!
element.encoded-hints: The "Oriental cafe", a Dublin institution. Table booking under my name.
